502
00:48:43,000 --> 00:48:46,830
 Growing these spiritual herbs and plants to about three hundred years old should be enough. 

503
00:48:46,830 --> 00:48:48,700
 If I concoct the pills based on the formulas in the book, 

504
00:48:48,700 --> 00:48:50,590
 I'll have ample supplies for consumption. 

505
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:03,800
 These should be enough. 

506
00:49:12,700 --> 00:49:14,700
Yellow Dragon Pill can strengthen my power.

507
00:49:14,700 --> 00:49:16,960
Golden Marrow Pill can transform mortal bones into immortal bones.

508
00:49:16,960 --> 00:49:20,450
If I take them together, their effect will be amazing.

509
00:50:02,300 --> 00:50:03,490
 This is bad. 

510
00:50:03,490 --> 00:50:04,900
 If this carries on, 

511
00:50:04,900 --> 00:50:06,950
 my Meridian system will be overwhelmed by these herbs. 

512
00:50:06,950 --> 00:50:09,310
 I must quickly circulate my vital energy to make a breakthrough. 

513
00:50:32,460 --> 00:50:35,220
   

514
00:51:42,010 --> 00:51:44,629
 Is this Level Four? 

515
00:51:44,629 --> 00:51:49,960
 I can now understand the greatness of this chant. 

516
00:51:49,960 --> 00:51:52,660
 I can sense the breaths of things around me. 

517
00:51:53,333 --> 00:51:54,544
 No. 

518
00:51:54,544 --> 00:51:57,674
 Sensing them is not enough. 

519
00:52:30,570 --> 00:52:31,994
 Not enough. 

520
00:52:31,994 --> 00:52:33,905
 Still not enough. 

521
00:52:33,905 --> 00:52:37,762
 Perception alone is not enough to resist Physician Mo. 

522
00:52:37,762 --> 00:52:39,702
 I need to be stronger. 

523
00:52:56,900 --> 00:52:59,440
I kept you waiting for a long time, Junior Brother Han.

524
00:52:59,440 --> 00:53:01,660
Senior Brother Li, you're swift.

525
00:53:01,660 --> 00:53:04,010
But you still arrived first.

526
00:53:05,410 --> 00:53:07,710
This Violent Python Power is too brutal.

527
00:53:07,710 --> 00:53:09,660
It doesn't suit me.

528
00:53:09,660 --> 00:53:13,050
Do you have any smaller, gentler, and more subtle techniques?

529
00:53:13,050 --> 00:53:14,735
I do.

530
00:53:14,735 --> 00:53:17,566
Junior Brother Han, tell me honestly.

