For example, Smokescreen Step.

546
00:54:09,400 --> 00:54:11,800
Smokescreen Step?

547
00:54:11,800 --> 00:54:14,190
You want to learn my secret technique?

548
00:54:14,190 --> 00:54:16,210
Will you teach me or not?

549
00:54:16,930 --> 00:54:20,230
Just because I can use it with ease doesn't mean it's easy.

550
00:54:20,230 --> 00:54:24,070
