551
00:54:27,570 --> 00:54:30,240
I don't have much time,

552
00:54:30,240 --> 00:54:33,080
but I still want to learn from Senior Brother Li.

553
00:54:35,820 --> 00:54:37,510
Seems like I need to demonstrate a few moves

554
00:54:37,510 --> 00:54:39,630
to check if you'll give up.

555
00:54:39,630 --> 00:54:41,420
Watch carefully.

556
00:55:10,930 --> 00:55:12,590
 At this point, 

557
00:55:12,590 --> 00:55:15,920
 I'm not that gullible to believe that when I reach Level Four, 

558
00:55:15,920 --> 00:55:19,590
 Physician Mo will spare my life after treating him. 

559
00:55:19,590 --> 00:55:21,150
 At the crucial moment, 

